Just wrapped up a production of Shakespeare’s “Twlefth Night” with the @wallis_studio_ensemble  and I am so so grateful to have been able to do this play with my amazing cast and Director. Thank you to the @hudsontheatres for having us! Thank you for Everyone, Family and Friends who were able to make it to the play, truly truly grateful and to my grandparents and parents for constantly cheering me on, I love you and couldn’t do it without you💜
